quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  3,149,"Hey mon yo gom…óim…ďe, si on …óoftike …ďen heefer…ďe, …ďe ruttay on e batte [kaaferaaku] mon, waylito…óon ko on hayru…ďe(pertube)"
  3,150,"Si ko woni, ko Alla woni Gi…óo mon, ko KaŇčko woni mo∆ī∆īu…óo e walloo…ďe …ďe"
  3,151,"Arma Men Welloo kulol e nder …ďer…óe …ďen heefer…ďe, sabu ko …ďe kafidi Alla e kon ko O Jippinanaali hujja. Werde ma…ď…ďe ko ka yiite, bonii werde …ďen too√Īoo…ďe"
  3,152,"Gom…óii Alla Goonginanii on Fodoore Makko nden tuma nde warayno…óon …ďe e DuŇčayee Makko, haa nde cooy…óon lurru…óon e fiyaake …óen, yeddu…óon …ďaawo o hollii on ko yi…óu…óon. No e mon …ďen faalaa…ďe aduna, no e mon kadi …ďen faalaa…ďe laakara. Hooti O Yiili on e ma…ď…ďe fii yo O Ndaarndo on. Gom…óii O Yaafanike on. Alla ko Jom ∆Āural e dow gom…óim…ďe …ďen"
  3,153,"Tuma nde dogayno…óon on ye∆ī∆īitoaako hay e gooto, Nulaa…óo on no noddira on …ďaawo mon. Suno e hoore suno he…ďi on fii wata on sunito e kon ko laawii on wanaa e kon ko he…ďi on. Alla ko Humpitii…óo e golloton"
